# HKElectrocardiogram.SymptomsStatus.present

**Case**

The user added a symptom when they recorded the ECG.

## Declaration

```swift
case present
```

## Discussion

To access the symptoms, query for the [doc://com.apple.healthkit/documentation/HealthKit/HKCategorySample] samples associated with the electrocardiogram sample.

## Status

- **HKElectrocardiogram.SymptomsStatus.none**: The user didn’t experience any symptoms during the duration of the electrocardiogram reading.
- **HKElectrocardiogram.SymptomsStatus.notSet**: The user didn’t specify whether or not they experienced symptoms.
